1
00:00:10,940 --> 00:00:14,020
♪Love crosses every cycle
of life and death♪

2
00:00:14,300 --> 00:00:17,580
♪So let me fall with you♪

3
00:00:17,580 --> 00:00:20,420
♪All the noise of the mortal world♪

4
00:00:20,420 --> 00:00:24,060
♪Is nothing compared to her eyes♪

5
00:00:24,060 --> 00:00:27,180
♪Whoever said love itself is sin♪

6
00:00:27,380 --> 00:00:31,020
♪When a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlight♪

7
00:00:31,020 --> 00:00:34,180
♪Painting a banquet
of endless spring blooms♪

8
00:00:34,620 --> 00:00:35,700
♪How beautiful♪

9
00:00:35,700 --> 00:00:38,860
=Blooms for Her=

10
00:00:38,900 --> 00:00:41,820
=Episode 14=

11
00:00:42,119 --> 00:00:44,280
Break down the door!

12
00:00:47,079 --> 00:00:48,119
Princess Anhe,

13
00:00:48,240 --> 00:00:49,640
your secret meeting with...

14
00:00:58,679 --> 00:01:00,000
Prince Jinghe?

15
00:01:00,200 --> 00:01:01,399
What are you doing here?

16
00:01:09,400 --> 00:01:09,920
Hide!

17
00:01:12,159 --> 00:01:12,959
What?

18
00:01:13,640 --> 00:01:15,640
My consort and I are newlyweds.

19
00:01:15,879 --> 00:01:16,959
We were having fun.

20
00:01:17,359 --> 00:01:19,040
Yet you guys came to kick down my door

21
00:01:19,040 --> 00:01:20,319
with so many people.

22
00:01:20,719 --> 00:01:22,519
Why? To entertain us?

23
00:01:22,920 --> 00:01:24,760
I'm His Majesty's consort.

24
00:01:25,159 --> 00:01:27,200
That makes me kind of your mother.

25
00:01:27,480 --> 00:01:28,760
Such daytime lust.

26
00:01:29,159 --> 00:01:29,879
You really

27
00:01:30,359 --> 00:01:32,159
should be more mindful!

28
00:01:33,400 --> 00:01:34,120
Your Highness.

29
00:01:34,319 --> 00:01:35,680
It's his privacy.

30
00:01:35,879 --> 00:01:36,920
Is it my business?

31
00:01:37,319 --> 00:01:38,079
Ridiculous!

32
00:01:48,599 --> 00:01:49,840
Forgive me, Prince Jinghe.

33
00:01:50,239 --> 00:01:52,359
I received a secret tip

34
00:01:52,799 --> 00:01:54,760
that someone meant harm to Mei Lin,

35
00:01:55,000 --> 00:01:56,200
so I rushed here at once

36
00:01:56,200 --> 00:01:56,959
to guard her.

37
00:01:57,359 --> 00:01:59,519
You barged into my consort's chamber.

38
00:01:59,680 --> 00:02:00,680
That's too much.

39
00:02:00,680 --> 00:02:02,000
How do you

40
00:02:02,000 --> 00:02:04,120
plan to ease my anger?

41
00:02:04,560 --> 00:02:06,400
I'm Prince Xuanlie's consort.

42
00:02:07,040 --> 00:02:08,719
Even if it was all a misunderstanding,

43
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:10,120
Prince Jinghe,

44
00:02:10,280 --> 00:02:12,879
are you really going to
fall out with Prince Xuanlie

45
00:02:12,919 --> 00:02:14,800
over something so trivial?

46
00:02:16,840 --> 00:02:18,759
Threatening me with his name?

47
00:02:18,759 --> 00:02:19,719
You got a death wish.

48
00:02:20,039 --> 00:02:20,599
Guards!

49
00:02:20,800 --> 00:02:23,080
Make her bow
and apologize to my consort.

50
00:02:24,400 --> 00:02:25,240
Murong Jinghe,

51
00:02:25,719 --> 00:02:27,039
don't push your luck!

52
00:02:36,840 --> 00:02:37,639
Luomei,

53
00:02:38,360 --> 00:02:40,919
watch where you're going next time.

54
00:02:41,280 --> 00:02:42,680
Don't walk into the wrong room again.

55
00:02:42,680 --> 00:02:43,000
You!

56
00:02:43,000 --> 00:02:44,639
Princess Murong Luomei lacks virtue

57
00:02:44,639 --> 00:02:45,639
and has offended us.

58
00:02:46,240 --> 00:02:47,080
Take her back.

59
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,599
Make her kneel for 10 hours,

60
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:50,879
then return her to Prince Xuanlie.

61
00:02:57,560 --> 00:02:59,319
Thanks a lot.

62
00:03:00,479 --> 00:03:01,520
Why?

63
00:03:01,879 --> 00:03:03,759
Have I displeased you somehow?

64
00:03:04,400 --> 00:03:06,280
You even had time
to see another man today.

65
00:03:07,520 --> 00:03:09,159
That was an accident.

66
00:03:10,479 --> 00:03:12,560
Muye Luomei sees me
as a thorn in her side.

67
00:03:13,360 --> 00:03:14,479
I can guard against her once,

68
00:03:14,840 --> 00:03:15,800
but not forever.

69
00:03:18,280 --> 00:03:19,000
Your Highness,

70
00:03:19,360 --> 00:03:21,960
this was my foolish mistake.

71
00:03:22,400 --> 00:03:23,560
Mei Lin is innocent.

72
00:03:24,080 --> 00:03:26,240
I'm willing to accept the punishment.

73
00:03:27,080 --> 00:03:28,120
Good that you know.

74
00:03:28,479 --> 00:03:30,520
If His Highness hadn't arrived in time,

75
00:03:30,719 --> 00:03:32,520
we might have been beaten to death.

76
00:03:33,159 --> 00:03:33,759
Mei Lin,

77
00:03:33,879 --> 00:03:35,280
I was only worried about you.

78
00:03:35,759 --> 00:03:37,680
I don't need your useless concern.

79
00:03:38,080 --> 00:03:39,199
In this palace,

80
00:03:39,240 --> 00:03:41,439
you can't even protect yourself.

81
00:03:41,439 --> 00:03:43,000
Who are you to protect me?

82
00:03:43,479 --> 00:03:44,840
If you truly care,

83
00:03:44,879 --> 00:03:46,080
stay away from me.

84
00:03:46,280 --> 00:03:47,479
Don't drag me down.

85
00:03:58,159 --> 00:03:59,800
So you do care about him.

86
00:04:00,000 --> 00:04:01,520
Pushing him away with harsh words

87
00:04:01,520 --> 00:04:02,520
just to keep him safe.

88
00:04:02,919 --> 00:04:04,840
Does a useless crybaby really deserve

89
00:04:05,400 --> 00:04:07,039
this much effort from you?

90
00:04:12,159 --> 00:04:13,000
Can't help it.

91
00:04:13,520 --> 00:04:14,560
He sees me

92
00:04:14,560 --> 00:04:17,040
as a big sister all along.

93
00:04:17,360 --> 00:04:19,319
And he does care about me.

94
00:04:20,160 --> 00:04:20,959
Why don't you

95
00:04:24,079 --> 00:04:25,920
let me be in charge as well?

96
00:04:27,439 --> 00:04:28,319
Can't let you do that.

97
00:04:37,360 --> 00:04:37,920
Your Highness,

98
00:04:38,480 --> 00:04:39,600
here's the solid proof Prince Xuanlie

99
00:04:39,600 --> 00:04:40,519
embezzled 400,000 taels

100
00:04:40,680 --> 00:04:41,480
in army pay.

101
00:04:42,319 --> 00:04:43,759
Tomorrow at court, I'll present it

102
00:04:43,759 --> 00:04:44,680
before everyone

103
00:04:44,879 --> 00:04:45,839
and bring him down.

104
00:04:46,439 --> 00:04:47,839
That's a huge sum.

105
00:04:48,040 --> 00:04:49,439
(Border Army Supply Withdrawal Record)
Father surely isn't unaware of it.

106
00:04:49,920 --> 00:04:50,920
If it's exposed publicly,

107
00:04:51,399 --> 00:04:53,279
it won't just ruin Murong Xuanlie.

108
00:04:53,600 --> 00:04:54,959
You'll also disgrace Father.

109
00:04:56,759 --> 00:04:58,199
If I must risk my life to remonstrate

110
00:04:58,680 --> 00:05:00,360
and secure the borders of Daliang,

111
00:05:00,920 --> 00:05:02,040
I would die without regret.

112
00:05:07,319 --> 00:05:07,920
Your Highness,

113
00:05:08,399 --> 00:05:09,600
you must have heard

114
00:05:09,759 --> 00:05:11,079
what we just said.

115
00:05:13,800 --> 00:05:14,800
Take this sword hairpin.

116
00:05:15,040 --> 00:05:15,959
Consider it a gift.

117
00:05:16,439 --> 00:05:17,920
Its blade is coated with poison.

118
00:05:18,040 --> 00:05:19,519
Not a good weapon on the battlefield.

119
00:05:19,920 --> 00:05:21,240
But it may save your life

120
00:05:21,480 --> 00:05:22,800
in a critical moment.

121
00:05:28,120 --> 00:05:28,920
Your Highness,

122
00:05:29,639 --> 00:05:30,759
I'm just a civil official.

123
00:05:30,800 --> 00:05:31,759
I once believed

124
00:05:32,160 --> 00:05:34,680
the court was full of scheming cowards

125
00:05:34,920 --> 00:05:36,120
who only feared death.

126
00:05:36,720 --> 00:05:37,759
But today,

127
00:05:38,279 --> 00:05:39,959
you have changed my view.

128
00:05:40,199 --> 00:05:42,279
Please take care of yourself

129
00:05:42,439 --> 00:05:44,519
and be an official
who serves the people.

130
00:05:48,920 --> 00:05:50,439
I'll keep that in mind.

131
00:05:54,759 --> 00:05:55,560
(Virtue Shines)
Your Majesty,

132
00:05:56,000 --> 00:05:57,759
Prince Murong Xuanlie embezzled

133
00:05:57,759 --> 00:05:59,519
400,000 taels from the border army's pay

134
00:05:59,839 --> 00:06:01,480
and raised a private army,

135
00:06:01,639 --> 00:06:02,439
intending rebellion.

136
00:06:02,879 --> 00:06:04,199
I beg you to investigate!

137
00:06:06,639 --> 00:06:07,439
Father,

138
00:06:07,439 --> 00:06:08,839
these ledgers are forged.

139
00:06:08,920 --> 00:06:09,720
(Border Army Supply Withdrawal Record)
I'm innocent!

140
00:06:15,040 --> 00:06:16,000
Xuanlie,

141
00:06:16,360 --> 00:06:17,639
as the eldest prince,

142
00:06:17,720 --> 00:06:18,720
you let corruption

143
00:06:19,040 --> 00:06:20,399
fester on your watch.

144
00:06:20,800 --> 00:06:21,600
Your Majesty!

145
00:06:21,839 --> 00:06:23,000
Prince Xuanlie's crime

146
00:06:23,000 --> 00:06:24,560
is treason, a capital offense!

147
00:06:24,800 --> 00:06:25,800
Don't show any mercy!

148
00:06:27,040 --> 00:06:27,839
Pei Du,

149
00:06:28,720 --> 00:06:31,879
are you saying I'm being unfair?

150
00:06:34,959 --> 00:06:35,639
Father,

151
00:06:35,920 --> 00:06:37,959
Mr. Pei is simply devoted to the empire.

152
00:06:38,160 --> 00:06:39,959
He spoke out of momentary passion.

153
00:06:40,360 --> 00:06:41,639
Please don't blame him.

154
00:06:44,560 --> 00:06:46,439
Prince Xuanlie failed in discipline.

155
00:06:47,199 --> 00:06:49,079
He's grounded for half a month.

156
00:06:49,079 --> 00:06:49,720
You're dismissed.

157
00:06:51,920 --> 00:06:53,439
Farewell, Your Majesty.

158
00:07:03,879 --> 00:07:05,399
Pei Du is a good blade.

159
00:07:05,560 --> 00:07:07,279
Too bad he's too sharp.

160
00:07:08,399 --> 00:07:10,000
It seems

161
00:07:10,000 --> 00:07:11,800
I need to get rid of him.

162
00:07:15,279 --> 00:07:16,959
Jian, how did it go?

163
00:07:17,279 --> 00:07:18,199
At the court session,

164
00:07:18,439 --> 00:07:20,240
the Emperor favored Prince Xuanlie.

165
00:07:20,319 --> 00:07:21,560
He only grounded him.

166
00:07:25,319 --> 00:07:26,319
Looks like

167
00:07:27,959 --> 00:07:29,560
I'll have to handle this myself.

168
00:07:41,759 --> 00:07:42,560
Yiyi,

169
00:07:43,160 --> 00:07:44,480
you're here to see me.

170
00:07:45,120 --> 00:07:46,399
I regret it.

171
00:07:46,879 --> 00:07:49,160
I regret letting go of your hand

172
00:07:49,560 --> 00:07:50,800
for illusory power.

173
00:07:51,120 --> 00:07:52,160
You regret it?

174
00:07:52,160 --> 00:07:53,000
Too late!

175
00:07:54,040 --> 00:07:54,879
It wasn't me!

176
00:08:12,060 --> 00:08:14,020
♪Moonlight spills like quiet tides♪

177
00:08:14,270 --> 00:08:17,240
♪A celestial bird
brushes the mountain's edge♪

178
00:08:19,100 --> 00:08:20,580
♪Wings of light drift through the air♪

179
00:08:20,580 --> 00:08:24,260
♪Like blossoms that refuse to fade♪

180
00:08:25,040 --> 00:08:28,060
♪It asks no right or wrong♪

181
00:08:28,300 --> 00:08:31,060
♪Nor fears the turning of fate♪

182
00:08:32,180 --> 00:08:33,780
♪A trace of spring on the wind♪

183
00:08:33,860 --> 00:08:36,420
♪A whisper of a broken heart♪

184
00:08:38,300 --> 00:08:40,380
♪A farewell song unfolds♪

185
00:08:40,660 --> 00:08:43,580
♪Carrying every sorrow within it♪

186
00:08:43,980 --> 00:08:46,020
♪Karma weaves its endless thread♪

187
00:08:46,140 --> 00:08:49,980
♪And I would follow you
without turning back♪

188
00:08:50,460 --> 00:08:53,460
♪Life and death become
nothing sharp or final♪

189
00:08:53,780 --> 00:08:56,860
♪Love and hate are carried away
on the breeze♪

190
00:08:57,460 --> 00:08:59,660
♪Before freedom is ever reached♪

191
00:08:59,660 --> 00:09:02,700
♪One must first dissolve into tears♪

192
00:09:03,300 --> 00:09:06,380
♪Love crosses every cycle
of life and death♪

193
00:09:06,580 --> 00:09:09,700
♪So let me fall with you♪

194
00:09:09,900 --> 00:09:12,840
♪All the noise of the mortal world♪

195
00:09:12,940 --> 00:09:15,900
♪Is nothing compared to her eyes♪

196
00:09:16,500 --> 00:09:19,820
♪Whoever said love itself is sin♪

197
00:09:19,820 --> 00:09:23,460
♪When a heartbeat turns into
wind and moonlight♪

198
00:09:23,460 --> 00:09:26,140
♪Painting a banquet
of endless spring blooms♪

199
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:29,100
♪How beautiful♪

200
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:33,460
♪Two hearts leaning into one another♪

201
00:09:35,020 --> 00:09:36,980
♪Perfectly, impossibly right♪
